lead_paragraph: Trinet Corporate Realty Trust Inc. said today that it had acquired three office buildings in Silicon Valley for $52.3 million from an undisclosed seller. The San Francisco-based real estate investment trust said the buildings totaled 187,380 square feet on about 12.5 acres. Two of the buildings are leased to the 3Com Corporation and the other to Sun Microsystems Inc., all through October 2006.
abstract: Trinet Corporate Realty Trust Inc acquires three Silicon Valley, Calif, office buildings for $52.3 million (S)
